title: Healthenut Cafe and Juice Bar
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Organic, Raw, Western, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out
description: Organic live food cafe and juice bar, opened since March 2013. Offers a menu of raw food, fresh juices, and raw desserts. Its retail area features wholefood organic supplements, raw crackers and chips, and other goodies. Located 5 minutes off Hwy 401.
